text: Herlinde Beutlhauser (born 23 November 1936) is an Austrian alpine skier. She competed in the women's downhill at the 1960 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Austria Category:Alpine skiers at the 1960 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Salzburg (state)
